  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 1em;">

  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" height="100%" width="100%" style="margin:0;padding:0;height:100%;width:100%;background:#cce3f7;font-family:helvetica"><tbody><tr><td align="center" valign="top"><tr>
<!--     <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding:0; margin:0; width:100%;height:100%; background:#cce3f7; font-family:helvetica"><tbody><tr> -->
      <td align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse; padding: 0 15px 0 15px;">
      <table border="0px" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="450" style="background:#fff;border:0px solid #e44556;max-width:450px; color: #505050;">
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td align="center" height="20px" style="border-collapse:collapse;background:#cce3f7">
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="left" height="31px" style="color:#e44556; padding: 15px 20px 15px 20px; background:#fff">
              <%= image_tag attachments['bloon-logo.png'].url, alt: 'bloon', height: '31px' -%>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="center" height="1px" style="border-collapse:collapse;background:#cce3f7; padding: 0px 20px 0px 20px;">
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="left" style="border-collapse:collapse;background:#fff;padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%; text-align:left">
              <i>Hey there, <%= @invitor.name %> wants to hang out with you!</i>
              <br><br>
              Want to <a href="<%= @url %>" style="text-decoration:none; color:#F3253B;" target="_blank"><b><%= @gather.activity %></b></a> with <%= @to_invitees %><%= "?" if @gather.date.blank? && @gather.time.blank? && @gather.location.blank? %>
              <% if @gather.date.present? %>  
                <%= " on " + @gather.date.strftime("%A, %b %e") %><%= "?" if @gather.time.blank? && @gather.location.blank? %>
              <% end %>
              <% if @gather.time.present? %>
                <%= " @ " + @gather.time.strftime("%l:%M%p") %><%= "?" if @gather.location.blank? %>
              <% end%>
              <%= " at " + @gather.location + "?" if @gather.location.present? %>
              <%= " " + @gather.more_details + "." if @gather.more_details.present? %>
              <br><br>
              We'll only do it if at least <b><%= 1 + @gather.tilt %></b> of us join (Bloon lets us know if we reach this). If youâ€™re interested, <a href="<%= @url %>" style="text-decoration:none; color:#F3253B;" target="_blank">join here!</a>
              <br><br>
              Looking forward to it,
              <br>
              <%= @invitor.name.split(' ').first %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 0px 20px 20px 20px">
              <a style="background-color:#F3253B;color:#ffffff;display:inline-block;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;padding:10px 30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold" href="<%= @url %>" target="_blank">Check it out!</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="center" height="4px" style="border-collapse:collapse;background:#D6D7DB">
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="background:#cce3f7;border-collapse:collapse;padding: 15px 10px 15px 10px">
              <p style="font-size:12px;color:black">
                <b>How does Bloon work?</b>
                <br>
                1. <%= @invitor.name.split(' ').first %> invited <%= @gather.num_invited %> friends to <%= @gather.activity %>
                <br>
                2. If you're interested, let <%= @invitor.name.split(' ').first %> know through <%= link_to "Bloon", @url %>
                <br>
                3. If <%= @gather.tilt %>+ people join <%= @invitor.name.split(' ').first %>, they will be notified and put in a group text where they can figure out the details without bothering others
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="background:#cce3f7;border-collapse:collapse;">
              <p style="margin:0;padding:0;font-size:11px;color:#9a9a9a">
    <%= link_to "Join", @url %> <%= @invitor.name.split(' ').first %> on Bloon and easily organize more fun with friends.
    <br>&copy; 2013 Bloon Inc. San Francisco, CA | <a href="mailto:hello@bloon.us" style="font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">hello@bloon.us</a><br><br>
      </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </tbody>
      </table>
      </td>
<!--     </tr></tbody></table> -->
  </tbody></tr></td></tr></table>
  </body>
</html>



